title: #92Noon Friday Football Feast!
description: PA & Charch with Vikings WR Adam Thielen to start the show, NY Daily News' Pat Leonard with Giants minicamp intel, Lindsay Whalen joins a day before her jersey is retired by the Lynx and then the duo of Kevin Gorg & Brian Arrigoni are breaking down horses and hockey during the final hour!
